    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述教育LMS门户和StudentDB之间的交互流程。核心是学生提交作业时的状态变化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那初始状态应该是什么？是学生刚进入系统时的空闲状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，初始状态叫IDLE。学生从LMS门户进入后，先处于空闲等待状态。然后当他们开始写作业时，要触发一个状态转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解为：IDLE之后进入写作状态，转换条件是AW handshake，并且这个握手是跟StudentDB进行的。写作完成后返回IDLE，触发方是LMS门户。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "AW handshake",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "W complete",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。AW handshake是申请写入的握手协议，W complete是写入完成。两个转换的触发方要区分开——开始写作业时StudentDB授权，完成后LMS门户确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITING",
        "AW handshake",
        "W complete",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已绘制完成。状态图包含：从Education_LMS_Portal进入IDLE，IDLE经AW handshake转换到WRITING，WRITING经W complete返回IDLE。两个转换的触发系统已分别标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "AW handshake",
        "W complete",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，WRITING返回IDLE的条件描述需要调整。不是\"W complete\"，应该是\"W complete\"，我之前口误了。另外确认一下版本，我们用stateDiagram-v2。",
